en_179687_0	HE the President Maithripala Sirisena in his capacity as the Commander-in-Chief of the Armed Forces has extended the service of Major General Shavendra Silva, Chief of Staff till 31 December, effective from 22 June 2019.
en_179687_1	Major General Shavendra Silva is also the Colonel of the Regiment, Gajaba Regiment and Colonel of the Regiment, Commando Regiment.
en_179687_2	He was appointed to the office of Chief of Staff in 9 January 2019.
